dct_title_s: Lake Khovsgol National Park, map and guide / Conservation Ink ; text, photographs, design, editing, and production by Jeremy Schmidt and Ted Wood. (Map)
dct_description_sm: Shows boundaries, roads, and place-names on a remote-sensing photographic base. Relief shown by spot heights. "The aerial photographs used for this map were taken by the Landsat 7 satellite on September 22, 2002." Panel title. Includes text, statistical data, location map, and color illustrations. Ancillary remote-sensing maps: Darhat Valley and Jigleg Pass -- Lake Khovsgol and the Khoridol Saridag Range.
